videos.description: Tremont Waters is off the mark on a 3-ball, but Kavell Bibgy-Williams tracks it down and throws down a huge two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Bigby-Williams hammers down putback slam

videos.description: Ja'Vonte smart comes off a ball screen and has a wide-open lane, going untouched to the rim for a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Smart blows by defense for two-handed jam

videos.description: Naz Reid drives baseline and dumps it off to Emmitt Williams, who goes over Mike Parks Jr. for a nasty one-handed finish.
videos.headline: Williams elevates for posterizing slam

videos.description: Isaiah Maurice comes up with a big rejection down low, then Jeremiah Martin pushes in transition and lobs it up to Kyvon Davenport for a thunderous finish.
videos.headline: Tigers turn defense into offense with alley-oop flush

videos.description: Ja'vonte Smart skips a behind-the-back bounce pass to Naz Reid, who sets his feet and drains a triple to put the Tigers up 60-54.
videos.headline: Smart goes behind the back to Reid for 3

videos.description: Tremont Waters feeds Kavell Bigby-Williams for an alley-oop, then finds him again for a big finish in the post.
videos.headline: Waters hits Bigby-Williams for 2 straight dunks

videos.description: Naz Reid gets turned around and puts up a shot with his back to the basket, but somehow gets it to fall, making it 74-64 Tigers.
videos.headline: Reid hits ridiculous back-to-basket flip shot

videos.description: Skylar Mays draws the defense and makes a beautiful pass to Emmitt Williams, who throws down a vicious one-handed jam to make it 80-71 LSU with under a minute left.
videos.headline: Williams hammers home dagger slam dunk
